title.@value: Problem with clinical software without injury or harm

definition.@value: Software malfunction causing interruption in processing of patient orders, laboratory or other diagnostic results, data entry, electronic communication, or data output, but without documented injury or harm.

label.@value: Problem with clinical software without injury or harm
interruption of processing of patient orders without documentation of injury or harm
interruption of processing or receipt of laboratory or other diagnostic results without documented injury or harm
